        "text": "👋 *Mitra — Daily Tracker*\n\n*🍽️ Food*\n• Send a *photo* of your meal\n• `/food 2 rotis and dal` — log by text\n• `/food summary` — today's food \\+ water\n• `/food weekly` — last 7 days\n• `/food monthly` — last 30 days\n\n*💧 Water*\n• `/water` — log 1 glass \\(250ml\\)\n• `/water 2` — log 2 glasses \\(500ml\\)\n• `/water 500` — log 500ml direct\n• `/water summary` — today's water intake\n• `/water weekly` — last 7 days\n• `/water monthly` — last 30 days\n\n_Targets: 2000 kcal · 3000ml water_",
